1
00:01:38,500 --> 00:01:44,300
"Unfold"

2
00:01:45,200 --> 00:01:47,500
(Episode 7)

3
00:02:20,083 --> 00:02:21,333
Wear my clothes for now.

4
00:02:21,583 --> 00:02:23,083
Get changed and come have breakfast.

5
00:03:01,333 --> 00:03:02,333
Here.

6
00:03:03,708 --> 00:03:05,166
I've washed your clothes for you.

7
00:03:06,125 --> 00:03:07,708
I put the documents on the table.

8
00:03:08,875 --> 00:03:09,375
By the way,

9
00:03:09,500 --> 00:03:11,166
why do you carry a tape measure with you?

10
00:03:26,375 --> 00:03:27,375
This is a ledger.

11
00:03:28,166 --> 00:03:30,125
It contains records of organ trafficking.

12
00:03:37,166 --> 00:03:38,500
Since I was sixteen,

13
00:03:38,583 --> 00:03:40,041
he made me work as a cleaner.

14
00:03:41,208 --> 00:03:43,000
A third of the records in this ledger

15
00:03:43,208 --> 00:03:44,750
are related to organ trafficking.

16
00:03:45,541 --> 00:03:46,707
They made the bodies

17
00:03:46,708 --> 00:03:48,082
look like accidental deaths

18
00:03:48,083 --> 00:03:49,083
or suicides.

19
00:03:49,625 --> 00:03:51,000
Once they fooled the police,

20
00:03:51,541 --> 00:03:53,833
they had me do the final house cleaning.

21
00:03:56,291 --> 00:03:58,125
And I wasn't adopted either.

22
00:04:00,041 --> 00:04:01,291
He kidnapped me.

23
00:04:04,750 --> 00:04:06,430
This is all the information
from back then.

24
00:04:15,458 --> 00:04:16,625
Everything will get better.

25
00:04:24,083 --> 00:04:26,166
I will make them pay.

26
00:04:45,541 --> 00:04:47,261
Bai Che went to the police with the ledger.

27
00:04:47,375 --> 00:04:48,625
Now the port is locked down.

28
00:04:49,625 --> 00:04:51,105
The police won't find anything on us.

29
00:04:51,666 --> 00:04:53,083
Who cares about the police?

30
00:04:53,458 --> 00:04:55,434
With the port locked down,
how am I supposed to ship the goods?

31
00:04:55,458 --> 00:04:58,208
If I can't deliver on time,
how am I going to pay the penalty?

32
00:05:05,958 --> 00:05:06,958
Hello?

33
00:05:15,125 --> 00:05:16,845
No official announcement has been made yet,

34
00:05:17,041 --> 00:05:19,201
and they already dare to
squeeze us by thirty percent.

35
00:05:19,750 --> 00:05:20,291
How much

36
00:05:20,292 --> 00:05:21,416
time do we have left?

37
00:05:21,958 --> 00:05:22,958
Three days.

38
00:05:24,000 --> 00:05:25,250
If we can't clear this up,

39
00:05:25,625 --> 00:05:26,825
we'll have to pay the penalty.

40
00:05:27,041 --> 00:05:28,041
If we do,

41
00:05:28,166 --> 00:05:29,926
the deal goes through
at the original price.

42
00:05:30,083 --> 00:05:31,083
Then,

43
00:05:31,208 --> 00:05:32,208
what about Bai Che?

44
00:05:32,541 --> 00:05:33,625
What do you want to do?

45
00:05:33,958 --> 00:05:36,083
First, buy back the shares
from those old geezers.

46
00:05:36,250 --> 00:05:37,666
Leave Bai Che alone for now.

47
00:05:39,000 --> 00:05:40,000
Alright.

48
00:05:50,208 --> 00:05:51,416
Then it's settled.

49
00:05:55,416 --> 00:05:55,958
A'Che,

50
00:05:55,958 --> 00:05:56,958
you're back.

51
00:05:58,541 --> 00:05:59,833
The police were just here.

52
00:06:00,083 --> 00:06:01,363
They were asking about the boss.

53
00:06:01,833 --> 00:06:02,833
They said

54
00:06:02,834 --> 00:06:04,875
the boss was murdered.

55
00:06:07,291 --> 00:06:08,083
We know.

56
00:06:08,250 --> 00:06:09,083
These past few days,

57
00:06:09,084 --> 00:06:10,666
we've been dealing with this too.

58
00:06:11,416 --> 00:06:13,522
I wanted to tell you,
the bookstore will be closed for now.

59
00:06:17,166 --> 00:06:18,326
Don't worry, Sister Xiao Yun.

60
00:06:19,500 --> 00:06:20,749
If you're really scared,

61
00:06:20,750 --> 00:06:21,990
you should go away for a while.

62
00:06:22,291 --> 00:06:23,291
A paid vacation.

63
00:06:24,416 --> 00:06:25,125
Sister Xiao Yun,

64
00:06:25,291 --> 00:06:26,809
the police will get to the bottom of this.

65
00:06:26,833 --> 00:06:28,625
Once it's on the news,

66
00:06:28,833 --> 00:06:29,958
you can come back.

67
00:06:31,250 --> 00:06:31,916
Then...

68
00:06:32,041 --> 00:06:33,375
I'll head home first.

69
00:06:59,958 --> 00:07:01,998
It's good for Sister Xiao
Yun to leave for a while.

70
00:07:02,375 --> 00:07:03,958
After all, those people are ruthless.

71
00:07:04,875 --> 00:07:05,875
Are you afraid

72
00:07:07,083 --> 00:07:08,250
they'll silence her?

73
00:07:10,208 --> 00:07:11,499
Is human life

74
00:07:11,500 --> 00:07:12,666
really that cheap to them?

75
00:07:15,500 --> 00:07:17,000
When Lao Bai kidnapped me back then,

76
00:07:17,541 --> 00:07:18,999
my parents' company

77
00:07:19,000 --> 00:07:20,000
was very influential.

78
00:07:20,583 --> 00:07:22,416
It caused a huge uproar in the city.

79
00:07:23,500 --> 00:07:25,875
But overnight,

80
00:07:26,166 --> 00:07:27,416
the tables turned.

81
00:07:28,291 --> 00:07:29,582
Public opinion condemned my parents

82
00:07:29,583 --> 00:07:31,083
for child neglect,

83
00:07:31,375 --> 00:07:32,625
leaving me with the elderly.

84
00:07:37,583 --> 00:07:39,303
The public backlash drove them to the edge,

85
00:07:39,333 --> 00:07:40,613
and they jumped to their deaths.

86
00:07:41,916 --> 00:07:43,041
Shortly after,

87
00:07:44,041 --> 00:07:45,416
my grandmother was driven mad too.

88
00:07:54,708 --> 00:07:55,791
Are you saying

89
00:07:56,243 --> 00:07:58,003
someone manipulated
public opinion back then

90
00:07:58,291 --> 00:07:59,750
to protect Lao Bai?

91
00:08:03,416 --> 00:08:05,208
My parents' deaths
were swept under the rug.

92
00:08:05,625 --> 00:08:07,124
People's attention was quickly

93
00:08:07,125 --> 00:08:08,583
diverted by other hot topics.

94
00:08:09,458 --> 00:08:10,583
It was as if

95
00:08:11,250 --> 00:08:13,083
this whole thing never happened.

96
00:08:16,041 --> 00:08:17,791
With Lao Bai's cautious nature,

97
00:08:18,041 --> 00:08:19,401
dealing with someone so dangerous,

98
00:08:19,958 --> 00:08:21,518
he would definitely have a backup plan.

99
00:08:24,291 --> 00:08:25,691
There's a small storeroom in there.

100
00:08:25,875 --> 00:08:27,059
Start searching from the inside.

101
00:08:27,083 --> 00:08:28,363
I'll search from the outside in.

102
00:08:39,583 --> 00:08:40,623
You haven't eaten all day.

103
00:08:41,041 --> 00:08:42,241
Let me cook something for you.

104
00:08:43,541 --> 00:08:44,541
I'm not hungry.

105
00:08:45,458 --> 00:08:46,708
Except for Bai Che,

106
00:08:47,000 --> 00:08:48,760
all the transfer contracts
have been signed.

107
00:08:51,500 --> 00:08:53,166
And now Bai Che has gone missing.

108
00:08:53,458 --> 00:08:55,041
The rumors online keep escalating,

109
00:08:56,000 --> 00:08:57,680
and dirt on the Zhao family is everywhere.

110
00:08:58,583 --> 00:09:00,083
To save his own skin, that man...

111
00:09:00,416 --> 00:09:01,416
whether it's Bai Che

112
00:09:01,458 --> 00:09:02,458
or us,

113
00:09:02,625 --> 00:09:03,625
we all have to die.

114
00:09:07,125 --> 00:09:08,125
That man?

115
00:09:10,083 --> 00:09:11,083
Yu Guangming.

116
00:09:12,083 --> 00:09:13,832
My old man and Lao Bai...

117
00:09:13,833 --> 00:09:15,500
That old bastard's good buddy,

118
00:09:17,833 --> 00:09:18,875
Yu Guangming.

119
00:09:20,541 --> 00:09:21,541
The mayor.

120
00:09:28,333 --> 00:09:30,041
The reason the Zhao family grew so fast,

121
00:09:31,000 --> 00:09:32,707
and why Lao Bai's dirty deeds

122
00:09:32,708 --> 00:09:33,916
never caused any trouble...

123
00:09:35,750 --> 00:09:37,125
Without Yu Guangming,

124
00:09:37,416 --> 00:09:39,166
they would have died dozens of times over.

125
00:09:43,166 --> 00:09:44,500
Now that Lao Bai is dead

126
00:09:46,166 --> 00:09:47,500
and Bai Che found the ledger,

127
00:09:50,000 --> 00:09:51,166
aren't they afraid?

128
00:09:51,791 --> 00:09:53,166
They're scared to death.

129
00:09:55,500 --> 00:09:56,625
So what do you plan to do?

130
00:10:14,458 --> 00:10:15,458
Cheng Fan,

131
00:10:16,375 --> 00:10:18,541
if I asked you to do
something very dangerous,

132
00:10:19,708 --> 00:10:20,708
would you do it?

133
00:10:21,000 --> 00:10:22,000
Yes.

134
00:10:25,291 --> 00:10:26,250
Without asking why?

135
00:10:26,250 --> 00:10:27,250
Without asking.

136
00:10:37,000 --> 00:10:38,000
Zhao Lingye,

137
00:10:38,958 --> 00:10:40,518
I need you to promise me one thing too.

138
00:10:40,875 --> 00:10:41,875
Name it.

139
00:10:47,916 --> 00:10:48,916
Don't die.

140
00:11:32,808 --> 00:11:34,201
[A letter from Yu
Guangming from 1965]

141
00:11:35,083 --> 00:11:36,333
Yu Guangming.

142
00:11:38,833 --> 00:11:39,833
Bai Che.

143
00:11:40,416 --> 00:11:41,416
Bai Che.

144
00:11:45,375 --> 00:11:46,375
Bai Che.

145
00:11:47,458 --> 00:11:48,458
Bai Che.

146
00:11:51,375 --> 00:11:51,958
Bai Che.

147
00:11:52,208 --> 00:11:53,208
Bai Che.

148
00:12:18,100 --> 00:12:23,700
(Unknown number: Come to
the abandoned building alone)

